parameters:
Did I... get transferred somewhere... and my body
can move?

I have been waiting for this moment for a long
time.
I have been searching for those who seek my power.
Don't play dumb... You're a demon, aren't you?

(No, wait... I can't possibly use such a great
power right after being summoned)

(Besides, you said you've been waiting for a long
time earlier.)

I am a member of the Hell Empire, one of the seven
kings.
I am the Jealousy King, Leviathan.
Then, make a contract with me.
Don't you want to start over?
Now, make a contract. Give me a kiss.

If making a contract with a demon... can save
Amelia.
(Who has time to choose a method?)
